selfOnboarding.title: Employee documents
selfOnboarding.description: During onboarding, employees will sign these documents.
selfOnboarding.directDepositDescription: Lets you pay the employee via direct deposit
selfOnboarding.includeI9Description: Verifies the employee's identity and work eligibility (must be completed onsite).

alerts.includedDescription: The federal government requires remote verification through a video call. You'll need to complete the verification process outside this application. Read the instructions.
alerts.includedDescription2: To avoid duplicate I-9 forms, deselect “employment eligibility” above.
alerts.notIncludedTitle: Have you completed the form I-9 already?
alerts.notIncludedDescription: If you are verifying the employee’s identity in person, select Form I-9 above. If verifying remotely, read <Link href="https://support.gusto.com/article/100165395100000/Complete-Form-I-9-and-E-Verify-for-new-hires" target="_blank">these instructions</Link> .

notSelfOnboarding.title: Employee documents
notSelfOnboarding.description: You will sign all these forms for your employee manually.
notSelfOnboarding.employmentEligibilityDescription: Verifies the employee's identity and work eligibility (must be completed on/by).
notSelfOnboarding.directDepositDescription: Lets you pay the employee via direct deposit
notSelfOnboarding.alertTitle: The government requires you to have Form I-9 and Form W-2 completed and signed.
